			Researchwork
			
			Weareworkingonsilicon/germaniumnanocrystals(silicon/germaniumnanoparticles,silicon/germaniumquantumdots)andsilicene/germanene.Computation,synthesis,characterizationandapplicationsinphotovoltaicsandoptoelectronicsareallintensivelycarriedout.

Thefollowingthreespecifictopicsarecurrentlyaddressed:
(1)Impurityeffect:dopantsandunintentionallyincorporatedimpurities.
(2)Surfaceeffect:inorganicandorganicligands.
(3)Printing-enabledfilms:solarcellsandlight-emittingdevices
			
				
